quran[21]{c,v,t,f}:
  56,82,"oo aad ka yeeleysaan (mahaddii) risiqiinna beenin (Xaqa)."
  56,83,"Maxaydaan markay (naftu) dhuunta gaadho."
  56,84,"Idinkuna markaas aad u jeeddaan (qofka dhiman)."
  67,22,"Ma mid socda wejigiisoo foorara baa hanuunsan, mise mid ugu socda si quman Jid Toosan?"
  67,23,"Dheh: (Alle) waa Kan idin uumay idiinna yeelay maqalka, aragga iyo laabaha. Yaraa intaad (ku) mahdisaan."
  67,24,"Dheh: (Alle) waa Kan idinku fidshay (abuuray) dhulka, Xaggiisaana la idiin soo kulmin (Qiyaamada)."
  68,16,"Waxaanu ka calaameyn sanqaroorka dushiisa."
  68,17,"Waxaanu u imtixaannay sidaanu u imtixaannay qoladii iska lahaa beerta, markay ku dhaarteen inay goosanayaan midhaha aroorta hore."
  68,18,"Iyagoon qayb u dhigin (saboolka), dhihinna inshaa Allaah (haddii Alle idmo)."
  69,13,"Marka Buunka (Qiyaame) la afuufo afuufid keliya (afuufka hore),"
  69,14,"Dhulka iyo buurahana laga rujiyo meelahooda, oo la baduugo baduugid mar keliya ah."
  69,15,"Maalintaa bay Dhacdada (Weyn) dhici (Qiyaamada)."
  70,7,"Annaguse waxaan u aragnaa inuu dhow yahay."
  70,8,"Maalintay samadu noqon sida maar shuban."
  70,9,"Buuruhu noqon sida cudbi la dhilay."
  71,4,"Wuxuu 'Alle' idiin dhaafi denbiyadiinna, oo idiin dib dhigi ilaa muddo magacaaban. Ajasha Alle (mowdku) markuu yimaado lama dib dhigo, waase haddaad og tihiin."
  71,5,"(Nuux) wuxuu yidhi: Rabbiyow! Waxaan qolodeydii ugu baaqay (Towxiid iyo falasho camallo san) habeen iyo maalinba."
  71,6,"Ha yeeshee baaqeygu uma uusan kordhin waxaan aheyn didmo."
  72,1,"(Nabi Muxammadow) dheh: Waxaa la ii waxyooday inay koox Jin ahi dhegaysteen (Qur’aanka). Markaasay yidhaahdeen: Waxaanu maqallay Qur'aan cajab leh.",1:[Al-Jin: Jinka, waa nooc ka mid ah uunka uu Alle ka abuuray (aabbahood Ibliis) dab oo indhaha dadka ka qarsoon.]
  72,2,"Oo ku hanuunin dhabbaha toosan abbaarta ah, markaasaan rumeynay,umana shariig yeeleyno cidna Rabbigayo (Allaah)."
  72,3,"Waxaa sarreeya Sharafta iyo Haybadda (Alle) Rabbigeen, ma uusan yeelan xaas iyo ilmo midna{2}.",1:[. Waxay qaarkood rumeysnaayeen jinku inuu Allaah leeyahay xaas iyo ilmo, laakiin kaddib markay soo Islameen waa ka hareen odhaahdaasi xun iyo caqiidadaas gurracan oo ka hufeen Alle inuu leeyahay wiil ama gabdho ama shariigyo.],2:[]
